body: Further adaptations and test changes for PyPy. There's certainly more left to do, but that doesn't mean we should wait to get these in.

commit.message:
prevent direct usage of PyWrapperDescrObject struct when not building in CPython

--HG--
extra : rebase_source : 1ada6cc5efa5fa3100aa0be920245afe0b37c163

make sure the global __pyx_b reference to builtins module is being kept alive in PyPy

--HG--
extra : rebase_source : dabba307e50ecd4a686f05e86dea8897c340f36d

use print() function in PyPy instead of trying to get at sys.stdout for printing

--HG--
extra : rebase_source : 7b2bd9cdc5254609b97aa1e6a4b175e201064c40

ignore CPython specific code in __Pyx_Generator_del() when not compiling for CPython

--HG--
extra : rebase_source : 33e7ac86a6ba0fb228299d3138fbeeced77ffbb1

disable string type checking for keyword arguments on PyPy because it does this at call time automatically

--HG--
extra : rebase_source : 1c3761bdab3fd0fed980dd9e44e5fdc4d22553b0

several PyPy specific fixes, originally proposed/encouraged by Amaury Forgeot d'Arc

--HG--
extra : rebase_source : a03ca7427bd5c6369583d12f1924b56f944e55aa

moved __Pyx_Method_ClassMethod() utility function into utility code file CythonFunction.c

--HG--
extra : rebase_source : 6312fa97e2f7f31a635466f2c64135da20531963

removed unnecessary global constant

--HG--
extra : rebase_source : 9a035ac0c9e7a4b810aad2900046ecde73a3111d

avoid using borrowed references for PyPy in __Pyx_unpack_tuple2() utility function

--HG--
extra : rebase_source : c458b30a48dfe984ddac7b5e939e01d31f0c458b
avoid using unnecessarily specialised C-API function PyMapping_DelItem()
disable generator frame juggeling in PyPy (not currently supported there)
change doctest to work with PyPy
avoid using sys.getrefcount() where possible (PyPy doesn't have it)
copied PyCFunction_Call() from CPython to be used when compiling for PyPy
used copied CPython PyCFunction_Call() function also for fused functions in PyPy
avoid unnecessarily unsafe code in test: don't take char* from global Python variable

title: Better support for PyPy's cpyext C-API
